title: Xfer Serum v1.0.0+KEYGEN+UPDATES
description:
Work with 64 and 32 bit.

1. Install V1.0.0

2. Go to v1.07b3 folder and patch fix, copy files and replace in vstplugin directory. (C:Program Files (x86)VSTPlugIns or
C:Program FilesVSTPlugIns) The 64bit patch works.

3. Now boot up Ableton.

4. Run Keygen from v1.0.0 folder, copy key.

5. Close Ableton and install v1.0.1b3 update.

6. Enjoy! If need you to keep entering serial everytime you load ableton then try copying the patch fixs over to the installed vst folder
